OL,3,CNew guidance as ministers 'ban' mobile
OL,4,Cphones in schools
OL,6,FIn England, it is currently up to
OL,7,Findividual heads to decide their own
OL,8,Fpolicies on mobile phones and whether
OL,9,Fthey should be banned
OL,11,FSchools in England have been issued
OL,12,Fnew guidance by ministers to ban
OL,13,Fmobile phones in schools.
OL,15,FThe Department of Educations say the
OL,16,Fmove would ensure consistency in
OL,17,Fclassrooms across England.
