OL,3,CNew guidance as ministers 'ban' mobile
OL,4,Cphones in schools
OL,6,FIt also suggests staff could search
OL,7,Fpupils and their bags for mobile
OL,8,Fphones if necessary, noting that
OL,9,F"headteachers can and should identify
OL,10,Fmobile phones and similar devices as
OL,11,Fsomething that may be searched for in
OL,12,Ftheir school behaviour policy".
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Gillian Keegan
OL,15,Fsaid the new guidance was a
OL,16,Fsignificant step, after originally
OL,17,Fpromising ban mobile phones in schools
OL,18,Fat last October's Tory conference.
