OL,3,CNew guidance as ministers 'ban' mobile
OL,4,Cphones in schools
OL,6,FThe promise was met with scepticism at
OL,7,Fthe time, and one trade union on
OL,8,FMonday branded it a "non-policy for a
OL,9,Fnon-problem".
OL,11,FOn an exclusive visit to a school with
OL,12,FITV News, Gillian Keegan said "we're
OL,13,Ftrying to introduce a consistent
OL,14,Fpicture across all of our schools, and
OL,15,Fto make sure that we reset the social
OL,16,Fnorm - that when you're in school,
OL,17,Ffrom the moment you arrive to the
OL,18,Fmoment you leave, you will not be
OL,19,Fpermitted to use your mobile phone".
