OL,6,FThe new guidance ranges from a total
OL,7,Fban on phones on school premises,
OL,8,Fstudents having to hand in their
OL,9,Fdevices at the start of the school day
OL,10,For keeping them in lockers, to pupils
OL,11,Fbeing trusted to keep their phones but
OL,12,Fon the condition they are not used.
