OL,6,FWhen asked by Susannah Reid if the
OL,7,Fdepartment was just "repeating
OL,8,Fguidance" they had previously
OL,9,Fannounced, the education secretary
OL,10,Finsisted she is here to "here to help
OL,11,Fheadteachers, not to do things that
OL,12,Fdon't make a difference to them".
OL,14,FThe government have gone back and
OL,15,Fforth on plans to ban mobile phones
OL,16,Ffor years.
