OL,3,CNew guidance as ministers 'ban' mobile
OL,4,Cphones in schools
OL,6,FIn 2021, then Education Secretary
OL,7,FGavin Williamson said he wanted to ban
OL,8,Fmobile phones in classrooms, but this
OL,9,Fidea was then scrapped by his
OL,10,Fsuccessor Nadhim Zahawi.
OL,12,FThe announcement comes after , to ban
OL,13,Funder 16s from owning a phone.
OL,15,FAlmost to remove social media apps
OL,16,Ffrom children's phones.
OL,18,FHellena Rose, a parent who spoke to
OL,19,FITV News said it was important for
OL,20,Fchildren to have access to phones in
OL,21,Fschools for "safety" reasons.
