OL,3,CNew guidance as ministers 'ban' mobile
OL,4,Cphones in schools
OL,6,FMs Rose said mobile phones can be a
OL,7,F"window into the school for parents",
OL,8,Foffering the children a form of
OL,9,F"protection" if an incident occurs at
OL,10,Fschool.
OL,12,FThe government pointed to recent
OL,13,Fofficial data that showed 29% of
OL,14,Fsecondary school pupils reported
OL,15,Fmobile phones being used when not
OL,16,Fsupposed to.
OL,18,FThey also revealed that 97% of 12-year-
OL,19,Folds currently own a mobile phone,
OL,20,Faccording to Ofcom figures.
