OL,3,CNew guidance as ministers 'ban' mobile
OL,4,Cphones in schools
OL,6,FBut the Association of School and
OL,7,FCollege Leaders said it did not expect
OL,8,Fthe new guidance to make any
OL,9,Fdiscernible impact.
OL,11,FGeneral Secretary Geoff Barton said
OL,12,Fthat the "compulsive use" of devices
OL,13,Fwas not happening in schools but
OL,14,F"while children are out of school".
OL,16,FHe said: "Most schools already forbid
OL,17,Fthe use of mobile phones during the
OL,18,Fschool day or allow their use only in
OL,19,Flimited and stipulated circumstances.
